lead_paragraph: Aides in former President Bill Clinton's White House crafted a strategy to "humanize" then-first lady Hillary Clinton and work around her "aversion" to the national media, according to documents released on Friday.

headline.main: Documents Show 1990s Effort to 'Humanize' Hillary Clinton
